title: Frank Schwab on NFL Season Best Bets (Win Totals, Player Props) (Football 07/02)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Frank Schwab of Yahoo! Sports, and the guys take a pretend $1000 budget to bet on season-long bets like win totals for various NFL teams and different player props for the full season.
